      <title>美国警告报告后乌克兰为俄罗斯石油袭击辩护</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-22/ukraine-defends-russian-oil-strikes-after-report-of-us-warning</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰高级官员为基辅对俄罗斯领土深处石油基础设施的袭击进行了辩护，此前有报道称，美国官员因油价飙升和克里姆林宫可能进行报复而警告不要进行此次行动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-22/ukraine-defends-russian-oil-strikes-after-report-of-us-warning</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Mar 2024 13:50:21 GMT</pubDate>
