    <item>
      <title>勒梅尔称法国将在不增加税收的情况下实现赤字目标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-22/le-maire-says-france-to-meet-deficit-goal-without-tax-increases</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国财政部长布鲁诺·勒梅尔表示，尽管经济增长疲弱和税收收入令人失望，破坏了最初的计划，但政府将在不提高税收的情况下实现控制预算赤字的目标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-22/le-maire-says-france-to-meet-deficit-goal-without-tax-increases</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Mar 2024 12:51:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>荷兰加大对联合利华 170 亿欧元冰淇淋上市的压力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-22/dutch-ramp-up-pressure-on-unilever-for-17-billion-ice-cream-listing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[荷兰政府正在游说联合利华公司 (Unilever Plc) 在荷兰上市其 170 亿欧元（合 184 亿美元）的冰淇淋部门，这家消费品巨头首席执行官本周早些时候发表的言论受到鼓舞。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-22/dutch-ramp-up-pressure-on-unilever-for-17-billion-ice-cream-listing</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Mar 2024 12:12:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国通过32亿欧元法案减轻企业负担</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-22/germany-passes-3-2-billion-bill-to-ease-burden-on-companies</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国议会上院通过了一项稀释后的法案，为企业提供 32 亿欧元（35 亿美元）的减税措施，结束了联合政府、联邦各州和主要反对党之间数月的争执。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-22/germany-passes-3-2-billion-bill-to-ease-burden-on-companies</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Mar 2024 11:34:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>创纪录的俄罗斯导弹袭击扰乱了乌克兰电力系统</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-22/ukraine-says-russian-missiles-struck-power-network-across-nation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰能源基础设施遭受自 2022 年俄罗斯入侵以来最大规模的导弹和无人机袭击，导致乌克兰多个地区停电，促使总统泽连斯基再次敦促外国盟友加快军事援助。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-22/ukraine-says-russian-missiles-struck-power-network-across-nation</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Mar 2024 05:57:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>波兰立法者预计对央行行长进行长期调查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-22/polish-lawmaker-expects-lengthy-probe-of-central-bank-governor</link>
      <description><![CDATA[波兰执政联盟正在准备对央行行长亚当·格拉平斯基(Adam Glapinski)进行旷日持久的调查，因为他的支持者（目前属于反对党）试图阻止可能导致行长下台的努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-22/polish-lawmaker-expects-lengthy-probe-of-central-bank-governor</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Mar 2024 05:00:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟监管机构人手不足，可能导致加密货币规则滞后</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-22/mica-implementation-eu-in-danger-of-falling-behind-on-prep-work</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟在监管加密货币的关键努力方面面临着落后的风险，因为其证券监管机构缺乏资源来足够快地评估加密货币对金融市场的潜在影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-22/mica-implementation-eu-in-danger-of-falling-behind-on-prep-work</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Mar 2024 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
